  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continue the Journey of Leo in DNA: Season 2...</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755719483\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755719483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755719483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Continue DNA in Season 2 as Leo's life has completely changed from the loss of his wife Luna to the hand of Terius.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0aca64bb4f3cbe75089df720751730e4.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play Through a Jungle No Man Dares to Enter...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through the unforgiving Saltus Forest jungle as he searches for Terius.<br><br></li><li>Play through rewarding challenges fueled by vengeance.<br><br></li><li> Fight against genetically modified creatures that have been experimented on by Nova Corp...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/52e20696cdc3088618b9f0589b4585a9.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fuel Your Vengeance...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick back up this season with DNA's epic 2D Beat'em up gameplay with new abilities to acquire!<br><br></li><li>Experience a challenging gameplay formula building upon last season's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Battle diverse creatures as you make your way through the dangerous Saltus Forest jungles. </li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/c10655af8ffb2d73134cb014c172c704.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Nemesis.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in Season 2: Episode 1 of DNA.<br><br></li><li>Search for your great nemesis Terius, in a challenging level of intense difficulty and grit.<br><br></li><li> Fight through a jungle of unknown creatures from experiments left to past... </li></ul></i>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continue the Journey of Leo in DNA: Season 2...</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755719483\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755719483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755719483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Continue DNA in Season 2 as Leo's life has completely changed from the loss of his wife Luna to the hand of Terius.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/0aca64bb4f3cbe75089df720751730e4.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play Through a Jungle No Man Dares to Enter...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through the unforgiving Saltus Forest jungle as he searches for Terius.<br><br></li><li>Play through rewarding challenges fueled by vengeance.<br><br></li><li> Fight against genetically modified creatures that have been experimented on by Nova Corp...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/52e20696cdc3088618b9f0589b4585a9.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fuel Your Vengeance...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick back up this season with DNA's epic 2D Beat'em up gameplay with new abilities to acquire!<br><br></li><li>Experience a challenging gameplay formula building upon last season's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Battle diverse creatures as you make your way through the dangerous Saltus Forest jungles. </li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953700/extras/c10655af8ffb2d73134cb014c172c704.avif?t=1755719483\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Nemesis.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in Season 2: Episode 1 of DNA.<br><br></li><li>Search for your great nemesis Terius, in a challenging level of intense difficulty and grit.<br><br></li><li> Fight through a jungle of unknown creatures from experiments left to past... </li></ul></i>",
